# NoX Settings
Package: whiteroom-nox-settings
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         whiteroom-common-settings
Description: provide default noX settings
 Provides default settings for appearance and applications of noX
 in siduction.
 .
 This overrides nox's defaults used for new users, all settings remain
 configurable by the local user and don't override already existing user
 profiles.

Package: whiteroom-nox-livesettings
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         whiteroom-common-livesettings,
         whiteroom-nox-settings
Description: noX settings in live mode
 Provides default settings for appearance and applications in noX live mode.
